snippet.title: Teen Daze
snippet.description:
Teen Daze is an electronic artist from the Fraser Valley, in British Columbia, Canada.

Listen to new single Translation: https://teendaze.lnk.to/Translation
New album 'Interior' out December 10th, 2021
